---
title: Cal Smart Hoisin-Ginger Tofu  with Savoury Rice and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: This classic Southeast Asian-inspired combo of tender tofu, savoury rice and spicy sauce is full of flavour but surprisingly light. Don't forget to drizzle sauce over every bite.

